      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Conferences\" title=\"Conferences\">Conferences</a> * Advances in Computer Games 10</b>\n</p><p><b><a href=\"/Advances_in_Computer_Games_9\" title=\"Advances in Computer Games 9\">&lt; Prev</a> <a href=\"/Advances_in_Computer_Games_11\" title=\"Advances in Computer Games 11\">Next &gt;</a></b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"http://icga.leidenuniv.nl/icga/news/Olympiad/Olympiad2003/fotos/graz_web/03.html\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/34/DomimBergWCCC2003.jpg/300px-DomimBergWCCC2003.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/3/34/DomimBergWCCC2003.jpg 1.5x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:DomimBergWCCC2003.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Dom im Berg  <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div>\n<p>The <b>10th Advances in Computer Games</b> Conference (ACG) took place at November 24-27, <a href=\"/Timeline#2003\" title=\"Timeline\">2003</a>, in <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Grazer_Schlo%C3%9Fberg\">Dom im Berg</a> in <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Graz\">Graz</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/European_Capital_of_Culture\">European Capital of Culture</a> in 2003, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Austria\">Austria</a>, in conjunction with the <a href=\"/WCCC_2003\" title=\"WCCC 2003\">11th World Computer Chess Championship</a> and the <a href=\"/8th_Computer_Olympiad\" title=\"8th Computer Olympiad\">8th Computer Olympiad</a>. ACG is the conference of the <a href=\"/ICGA\" title=\"ICGA\">ICGA</a>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Photos\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Photos</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Conference_Proceedings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Conference Proceedings</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Lectures\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Lectures</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Reports\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Reports</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">7</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Photos\">Photos</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Advances_in_Computer_Games_10&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Photos\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"http://www.yss-aya.com/photo/graz2003/1125/Htmls/PICT1180.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"ACG10DomamBerg.jpg\" src=\"/images/c/c4/ACG10DomamBerg.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\" style=\"vertical-align: text-bottom\" class=\"thumbborder\" /></a></div> \n<p>Conference in the cave <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Conference_Proceedings\">Conference Proceedings</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Advances_in_Computer_Games_10&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Conference Proceedings\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <b>Advances in Computer Games 10</b></li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a href=\"/Jaap_van_den_Herik\" title=\"Jaap van den Herik\">Jaap van den Herik</a>, <a href=\"/Hiroyuki_Iida\" title=\"Hiroyuki Iida\">Hiroyuki Iida</a> and <a href=\"/Ernst_A._Heinz\" title=\"Ernst A. Heinz\">Ernst A. Heinz</a> (eds.) (<b>2004</b>)</dd>\n<dd> Series: <a href=\"/IFIP\" title=\"IFIP\">IFIP</a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.springer.com/series/6102\">Advances in Information and Communication Technology</a>, Vol. 135</dd>\n<dd> ISBN: 978-1-4020-7709-8</dd></dl>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Lectures\">Lectures</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Advances_in_Computer_Games_10&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Lectures\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Dave_Gomboc\" title=\"Dave Gomboc\">Dave Gomboc</a>, <a href=\"/Tony_Marsland\" title=\"Tony Marsland\">Tony Marsland</a>, <a href=\"/Michael_Buro\" title=\"Michael Buro\">Michael Buro</a> (<b>2003</b>). <i>Evaluation Function Tuning via Ordinal Correlation</i>. <a href=\"/University_of_Alberta\" title=\"University of Alberta\">University of Alberta</a>, Edmonton, Alberta, Canada, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.top-5000.nl/ps/Dave%20Gomboc%20-%20Evaluation%20Tuning.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Albert_Xin_Jiang\" title=\"Albert Xin Jiang\">Albert Xin Jiang</a>, <a href=\"/Michael_Buro\" title=\"Michael Buro\">Michael Buro</a> (<b>2003</b>). <i>First Experimental Results of ProbCut Applied to Chess</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://cs.ubc.ca/%7Ejiang/papers/mpc_main.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Aleksander_Sadikov\" title=\"Aleksander Sadikov\">Aleksander Sadikov</a>, <a href=\"/Ivan_Bratko\" title=\"Ivan Bratko\">Ivan Bratko</a>,  and <a href=\"/Igor_Kononenko\" title=\"Igor Kononenko\">Igor Kononenko</a> (<b>2003</b>). <i>Search versus Knowledge: An Empirical Study of Minimax on KRK</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.ailab.si/sasha/acg2003.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Darse_Billings\" title=\"Darse Billings\">Darse Billings</a>, <a href=\"/Yngvi_Bj%C3%B6rnsson\" title=\"Yngvi Björnsson\">Yngvi Björnsson</a> (<b>2003</b>). <i>Search and Knowledge in Lines of Action</i>.  <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://webdocs.cs.ualberta.ca/~darse/Papers/skloa-sub.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Jens_Lieberum\" title=\"Jens Lieberum\">Jens Lieberum</a> (<b>2003</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0304397505005979\">An Evaluation Function for the Game of Amazons</a></i>. </li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Jeroen_Donkers\" title=\"Jeroen Donkers\">Jeroen Donkers</a>, <a href=\"/Jaap_van_den_Herik\" title=\"Jaap van den Herik\">Jaap van den Herik</a>, and <a href=\"/Jos_Uiterwijk\" title=\"Jos Uiterwijk\">Jos Uiterwijk</a> (<b>2003</b>). <i>Opponent Models in Bao: Conditions of a Successfull Application</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.fdg.unimaas.nl/educ/donkers/pubs/..%5Cpdf%5Cacg10.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Akihiro_Kishimoto\" title=\"Akihiro Kishimoto\">Akihiro Kishimoto</a>, <a href=\"/Martin_M%C3%BCller\" title=\"Martin Müller\">Martin Müller</a>. (<b>2003</b>). <i>Df-pn in Go: An Application to the One-Eye Problem</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.fun.ac.jp/%7Ekishi/pdf_file/acg_kishimoto_mueller.pdf\">pdf</a>.</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Ryan_Hayward\" title=\"Ryan Hayward\">Ryan Hayward</a>, <a href=\"/Yngvi_Bj%C3%B6rnsson\" title=\"Yngvi Björnsson\">Yngvi Björnsson</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Michael_Johanson&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Michael Johanson (page does not exist)\">Michael Johanson</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Morgan_Kan&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Morgan Kan (page does not exist)\">Morgan Kan</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Nathan_Po&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Nathan Po (page does not exist)\">Nathan Po</a> and <a href=\"/index.php?title=Jack_van_Rijswijck&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Jack van Rijswijck (page does not exist)\">Jack van Rijswijck</a> (<b>2003</b>). <i>Solving 7x7 Hex: Virtual Connections and Game-state Reduction</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.ru.is/faculty/yngvi/pdf/HaywardBJKPR03.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Jonathan_Schaeffer\" title=\"Jonathan Schaeffer\">Jonathan Schaeffer</a>, <a href=\"/Yngvi_Bj%C3%B6rnsson\" title=\"Yngvi Björnsson\">Yngvi Björnsson</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Neil_Burch&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Neil Burch (page does not exist)\">Neil Burch</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Rob_Lake&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Rob Lake (page does not exist)\">Robert Lake</a>, <a href=\"/Paul_Lu\" title=\"Paul Lu\">Paul Lu</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php?title=Steve_Sutphen&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Steve Sutphen (page does not exist)\">Steve Sutphen</a> (<b>2003</b>). <i>Building the Checkers 10-Piece Endgame Databases.</i> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://webdocs.cs.ualberta.ca/%7Ejonathan/Grad/Papers/databases10.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Ed_Trice&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Ed Trice (page does not exist)\">Ed Trice</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Gil_Dodgen&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Gil Dodgen (page does not exist)\">Gil Dodgen</a> (<b>2003</b>). <i>The 7-Piece Perfect Play Lookup Database for the Game of Checkers</i>. </li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Markus_Enzenberger\" title=\"Markus Enzenberger\">Markus Enzenberger</a> (<b>2003</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://webdocs.cs.ualberta.ca/~emarkus/neurogo/neurogo3/index.html\">Evaluation in Go by a Neural Network using Soft Segmentation</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://webdocs.cs.ualberta.ca/~emarkus/publications/neurogo3.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Erik_van_der_Werf\" title=\"Erik van der Werf\">Erik van der Werf</a>, <a href=\"/Jaap_van_den_Herik\" title=\"Jaap van den Herik\">Jaap van den Herik</a>, <a href=\"/Jos_Uiterwijk\" title=\"Jos Uiterwijk\">Jos Uiterwijk</a> (<b>2003</b>). <i>Learning to Score Final Positions in the Game of Go</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://erikvanderwerf.tengen.nl/pubdown/learning_to_score.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Bruno_Bouzy\" title=\"Bruno Bouzy\">Bruno Bouzy</a>, <a href=\"/Bernard_Helmstetter\" title=\"Bernard Helmstetter\">Bernard Helmstetter</a> (<b>2003</b>). <i>Monte Carlo Go Developments</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.ai.univ-paris8.fr/~bh/articles/acg10-mcgo.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Bernard_Helmstetter\" title=\"Bernard Helmstetter\">Bernard Helmstetter</a>, <a href=\"/Tristan_Cazenave\" title=\"Tristan Cazenave\">Tristan Cazenave</a> (<b>2003</b>). <i>Searching with analysis of dependencies in a solitaire card game</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.lamsade.dauphine.fr/~cazenave/papers/acg10-solitaire.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.informatik.uni-trier.de/~ley/db/indices/a-tree/b/Bolognesi:Andrea.html\">Andrea Bolognesi</a>, <a href=\"/Paolo_Ciancarini\" title=\"Paolo Ciancarini\">Paolo Ciancarini</a> (<b>2003</b>). <i>Computer Programming of Kriegspiel Endings: The Case of KR vs. K</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.cs.unibo.it/~cianca/wwwpages/chesssite/kriegspiel/endings.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/John_Tamplin\" title=\"John Tamplin\">John Tamplin</a>, <a href=\"/Guy_Haworth\" title=\"Guy Haworth\">Guy Haworth</a> (<b>2003</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://centaur.reading.ac.uk/4547/\">Chess Endgames: Data and Strategy</a></i>. </li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Guy_Haworth\" title=\"Guy Haworth\">Guy Haworth</a>, <a href=\"/Rafael_B._Andrist\" title=\"Rafael B. Andrist\">Rafael B. Andrist</a> (<b>2003</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://centaur.reading.ac.uk/4548/\">Model Endgame Analysis</a></i>. </li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Tomoyuki_Kaneko\" title=\"Tomoyuki Kaneko\">Tomoyuki Kaneko</a>, <a href=\"/Kazunori_Yamaguchi\" title=\"Kazunori Yamaguchi\">Kazunori Yamaguchi</a>, <a href=\"/Satoru_Kawai\" title=\"Satoru Kawai\">Satoru Kawai</a> (<b>2003</b>). <i>Automated Identification of Patterns in Evaluation Functions for General Game Players</i>. </li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Reports\">Reports</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Advances_in_Computer_Games_10&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Reports\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Jan_Renze_Steenhuisen\" title=\"Jan Renze Steenhuisen\">Jan Renze Steenhuisen</a> (<b>2003</b>). <i>Report on the 10th Advances in Computer Games Conference</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#26_4\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 26, No. 4</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.st.ewi.tudelft.nl/%7Erenze/doc/ACG10-report.pdf\">pdf</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</spa